metadata.name: THE ROAR
metadata.description:
Scarry,,,,,,,,

Roaring seen of a tiger

The law of the jungle says that the one with the power will rule. And that's the exactly what the case here. Many stories and histories are associated with the life of arrowhead that can impress the beholders. T-84 (arrowhead) took control of the area, which was the territory of T-19, her mother, and also happens to the largest region in Ranthambore National Park. Years later, T-18 took was shifted to Sariska, and thats when T-19 even took over her territory.

This image was taken from Ranthambore Tiger Reserve, Rajasthan, India

Pic by Arjun ak

Using Nikon D500, Tamaron 150- 600mm

This photo NFT is 1 : 1
